WEBVTT

00:11.480 --> 00:12.590
You killed Tubu?

00:13.430 --> 00:14.000
Yes.

00:14.640 --> 00:15.960
He insulted the Consort,

00:15.960 --> 00:17.890
so I killed him in a moment of anger.

00:18.070 --> 00:19.350
I know I am at fault

00:19.830 --> 00:21.490
and am willing to be punished.

00:23.390 --> 00:24.590
Your Majesty is wise.

00:24.830 --> 00:26.390
You foresaw that they

00:26.390 --> 00:29.320
would not be peaceful
after the Pale Tribe incident.

00:29.550 --> 00:30.960
So you asked me to plant a few spies

00:30.960 --> 00:31.690
around them,

00:32.070 --> 00:33.670
and that prevented a major incident.

00:33.670 --> 00:34.470
Your Majesty.

00:35.600 --> 00:37.200
Tubu's family rose in power.

00:37.560 --> 00:39.280
The Hongchuan Tribe alone

00:39.280 --> 00:40.340
commands 10,000 elite cavalry.

00:40.340 --> 00:42.140
Now that he has died so suddenly,

00:42.920 --> 00:45.430
I fear it will cause unrest
among the tribes,

00:45.600 --> 00:48.240
making them think
Your Majesty is using this

00:48.520 --> 00:49.980
to eliminate dissidents.

01:10.510 --> 01:11.680
Well done.

01:14.590 --> 01:16.710
I have wanted to kill him for a long time.

01:16.710 --> 01:17.400
Rise.

01:44.509 --> 01:45.479
General Shiyan.

01:45.870 --> 01:46.759
You were right.

01:47.470 --> 01:49.240
I am indeed using this matter

01:50.020 --> 01:51.080
to eliminate them.

01:52.759 --> 01:53.590
Pass my order.

01:54.310 --> 01:55.120
Except for the Hongchuan Tribe

01:55.120 --> 01:57.509
and the offending tribe elders today,

01:58.070 --> 01:59.270
the rest of the tribes

01:59.509 --> 02:02.200
will be exempt from this year's
taxes and conscription.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.480
These old foxes—

02:04.350 --> 02:06.480
Which of them isn't shrewd

02:06.670 --> 02:07.800
and opportunistic?

02:08.400 --> 02:09.860
I am giving them benefits.

02:10.590 --> 02:11.710
I don't believe

02:12.560 --> 02:14.380
they would turn down what I offer,

02:14.380 --> 02:16.380
but rebel with the Hongchuan Tribe.

03:38.480 --> 03:43.750
[REBIRTH]

03:44.180 --> 03:46.790
[Episode 28]

03:56.400 --> 03:58.360
I have followed Your Highness's orders

03:58.360 --> 04:00.190
and washed Lord Cheng's cloak.

04:00.910 --> 04:03.570
But this bloodstain has seeped
into the lining.

04:03.920 --> 04:06.380
No matter how I wash it,
there's still a mark.

04:16.950 --> 04:18.410
Greetings, Your Majesty.

04:26.470 --> 04:27.930
Greetings, Your Majesty.

04:28.560 --> 04:29.890
This way, Your Majesty.

04:53.560 --> 04:54.690
You've been wronged

04:55.800 --> 04:57.270
by what happened a few days ago.

04:57.270 --> 04:59.270
Your Majesty has already stood up for me

04:59.270 --> 05:00.870
and punished the offenders.

05:01.510 --> 05:02.830
How could I feel wronged?

05:02.830 --> 05:03.750
I meant

05:04.600 --> 05:06.240
those rumors.

05:07.000 --> 05:08.480
All they were saying was

05:08.920 --> 05:10.780
that you're merely a figurehead,

05:11.160 --> 05:12.750
having the title of a Consort

05:12.750 --> 05:14.680
but having none of my favor—

05:16.350 --> 05:17.990
I even have no desire for you.

05:18.630 --> 05:20.310
If they didn't think so,

05:20.630 --> 05:22.600
they wouldn't dare treat you like this.

05:22.600 --> 05:23.430
Don't you

05:24.950 --> 05:26.120
feel wronged?

05:36.000 --> 05:37.159
I do not.

05:38.120 --> 05:40.120
I want to apologize to Your Majesty.

05:40.120 --> 05:42.520
Your Majesty has never
had feelings for me,

05:42.680 --> 05:45.190
and we have never
consummated our marriage.

05:45.430 --> 05:47.030
It was I who used every scheme

05:47.240 --> 05:49.510
and unbearable means
to seduce Your Majesty.

05:49.510 --> 05:50.950
Your Majesty wanted to silence

05:50.950 --> 05:53.240
the elders of the tribes in Great Yan,

05:53.600 --> 05:54.830
so you played along

05:55.430 --> 05:57.830
and granted me the title
of Consort Helian.

05:57.870 --> 05:59.670
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

05:59.780 --> 06:00.870
You were right.

06:01.480 --> 06:03.630
But you know those tribe elders
in Great Yan

06:03.630 --> 06:05.360
are trying everything they can

06:05.480 --> 06:07.070
to send their daughter

06:07.070 --> 06:08.270
to my side.

06:09.270 --> 06:09.880
Do you know

06:10.930 --> 06:12.200
why I chose you?

06:16.630 --> 06:19.950
The reason I schemed to get close
to Your Majesty

06:21.070 --> 06:22.930
was that the Helian Tribe is weak,

06:23.510 --> 06:26.430
struggling to survive
among the other tribes.

06:27.070 --> 06:29.330
I want to bring glory to the Helian Tribe.

06:29.470 --> 06:31.430
And Your Majesty chose me as your consort

06:31.430 --> 06:32.690
for this exact reason.

06:32.820 --> 06:34.550
A Consort from the Helian Tribe

06:35.510 --> 06:38.170
will neither break the balance
among the tribes

06:38.820 --> 06:41.670
nor pose a threat to Your Majesty.

06:55.390 --> 06:56.920
I will stay tonight.

06:57.590 --> 06:59.450
I didn't choose the wrong person.

06:59.790 --> 07:00.910
From now on,

07:01.680 --> 07:04.830
you're not only going to be someone
useful to the Helian Tribe,

07:04.830 --> 07:06.830
but also someone useful to me.

07:08.600 --> 07:09.630
Are you willing?

07:23.830 --> 07:25.360
Greetings, General Cheng.

07:25.430 --> 07:26.870
Is Consort Helian resting?

07:26.870 --> 07:27.730
General Cheng,

07:27.920 --> 07:29.750
His Majesty is spending
the night here today,

07:29.750 --> 07:31.350
and they went to sleep early.

07:31.870 --> 07:33.720
Is there something you need?

08:41.039 --> 08:43.630
[Zhenhuangcheng, Great Yong]

08:42.020 --> 08:43.789
The royal family is
on an ancestral worship journey.

08:43.789 --> 08:45.790
Clear the roads and close the doors.

08:46.270 --> 08:47.670
Anyone who dares to proceed

08:47.670 --> 08:48.670
will be executed!

08:58.270 --> 08:59.510
Stop, stop.

09:03.630 --> 09:04.490
Your Highness.

09:04.550 --> 09:05.630
You are pregnant.

09:05.750 --> 09:07.470
The journey will be too strenuous for you.

09:07.470 --> 09:09.630
Although you were brought back
by His Highness the Seventh Prince,

09:09.630 --> 09:11.120
the Thirteenth Prince is currently

09:11.120 --> 09:12.600
in His Majesty's favor.

09:12.790 --> 09:14.790
He is even handling
the royal ancestral worship,

09:14.790 --> 09:16.670
while His Highness the Seventh Prince
was punished by His Majesty

09:16.670 --> 09:19.000
and was sent to guard the border.

09:19.110 --> 09:20.700
Let's not get involved in this.

09:20.700 --> 09:24.100
We should keep a low profile
and return to the mansion to rest.

09:26.510 --> 09:27.960
You are quite clever.

09:28.320 --> 09:30.850
Thank you for the compliment,
Your Highness.

09:31.550 --> 09:32.860
Who could speak for me,

09:32.910 --> 09:34.110
and whose side I'm on—

09:34.180 --> 09:37.030
It is not something a lowly maid
like you can discuss.

09:37.030 --> 09:38.160
Move the palanquin.

09:43.510 --> 09:44.770
Who is blocking my way?

09:48.040 --> 09:51.290
[Jia Meng]

09:51.910 --> 09:54.440
Princess, you shouldn't care who I am,

09:54.720 --> 09:57.910
but rather what I can do for you.

09:58.120 --> 10:00.510
You are sinking into an abyss of pain,

10:00.750 --> 10:03.320
but I can let you see

10:03.320 --> 10:05.840
the person you miss.

10:09.380 --> 10:12.090
Omniscient and omnipotent Faceless God,

10:12.720 --> 10:15.000
as your most loyal follower,

10:15.240 --> 10:16.720
I pray to you.

10:17.150 --> 10:19.080
May you forgive his sins,

10:19.310 --> 10:20.980
take pity on his pain,

10:21.000 --> 10:24.600
and let the departed soul
return once more.

11:30.960 --> 11:31.750
Chun'er.

11:32.360 --> 11:33.150
I'm back.

11:48.720 --> 11:49.390
Li Yan.

11:50.200 --> 11:51.790
Can you hold me...

11:54.360 --> 11:55.790
and our child?

11:57.080 --> 11:58.790
Why did you leave me?

12:01.150 --> 12:02.960
Where did you go?

12:23.360 --> 12:25.240
I want you to stay with me.

12:25.640 --> 12:27.730
It's too painful to be alone.

12:29.390 --> 12:29.980
Chun'er.

12:32.150 --> 12:34.550
You are the most precious
and beloved person

12:34.550 --> 12:37.390
I have in this world.

12:38.030 --> 12:38.720
But

12:40.700 --> 12:43.150
I'm the only one left in this world now.

12:43.590 --> 12:45.250
Even you, right in front of me,

12:45.750 --> 12:47.440
are just my illusion.

12:48.030 --> 12:49.080
You know what?

12:51.910 --> 12:53.080
I'm so scared.

12:54.510 --> 12:55.670
I'm so cold.

12:58.200 --> 12:59.870
Can you hold me?

13:00.390 --> 13:01.390
Just once,

13:01.670 --> 13:02.840
for the last time.

13:03.960 --> 13:04.670
Chun'er.

13:06.750 --> 13:08.270
You have to live well.

13:10.030 --> 13:10.720
For me,

13:11.790 --> 13:13.510
and for our child.

13:25.600 --> 13:26.240
Li Yan.

13:28.390 --> 13:30.120
Li Yan!

13:36.150 --> 13:37.480
Li Yan!

13:54.200 --> 13:55.270
Chu Qiao,

13:56.200 --> 13:58.360
I will never let you go as long as I live!

14:06.670 --> 14:07.530
Your Highness,

14:08.030 --> 14:10.290
the Faceless God let His Highness leave.

14:10.390 --> 14:13.510
The Faceless God
is an omnipotent true god.

14:13.910 --> 14:16.110
As long as you devoutly believe in them,

14:16.270 --> 14:19.080
they can return the dead to you.

14:27.360 --> 14:29.600
I thought it was some amazing trick.

14:30.650 --> 14:33.290
Turns out you're just a lying sorcerer.

14:33.460 --> 14:35.190
It's nothing but a simple drug.

14:36.000 --> 14:38.360
Do you really think you can fool me?

14:39.860 --> 14:40.630
Your Highness.

14:40.630 --> 14:41.560
I wouldn't dare.

14:42.150 --> 14:44.320
I'm of low status.

14:44.320 --> 14:45.790
I'm just a follower of the Faceless God.

14:45.790 --> 14:47.360
I can't possess the power
of the Faceless God,

14:47.360 --> 14:49.480
so I resorted to using knockout drugs.

14:49.480 --> 14:52.480
But the Faceless God
is the almighty true god.

14:53.670 --> 14:55.070
You are a noble Princess,

14:55.120 --> 14:56.720
the chosen one,

14:56.850 --> 14:59.050
and someone closer to the Faceless God.

14:59.130 --> 15:01.300
If you devote yourself wholeheartedly
to the Faceless God,

15:01.300 --> 15:04.210
their will shall descend

15:04.480 --> 15:06.480
and fulfill all your desires.

15:12.960 --> 15:14.080
If so,

15:15.240 --> 15:16.750
why don't I take you to see

15:16.790 --> 15:18.870
someone closer to the Faceless God?

15:24.690 --> 15:26.090
Didn't I say

15:27.380 --> 15:29.260
only one of you can live?

15:30.030 --> 15:31.600
Why didn't you listen to me?

15:32.510 --> 15:33.640
How disappointing!

15:37.030 --> 15:38.390
Your Highness the Thirteenth Prince.

15:38.390 --> 15:41.750
I came to teach you
how to govern a country,

15:42.390 --> 15:43.870
I didn't come here to drink

15:44.440 --> 15:45.960
and feast with you,

15:46.270 --> 15:49.030
nor to watch you torture
and kill maidservants

15:49.390 --> 15:50.670
for fun.

15:51.600 --> 15:52.330
Grand Tutor,

15:53.080 --> 15:54.200
look clearly.

15:55.150 --> 15:56.840
I'm just practicing archery.

15:58.140 --> 15:59.600
This is hardly amusement.

16:00.440 --> 16:04.320
I never miss a shot. My aim is perfect.

16:05.840 --> 16:07.390
Your Highness the Thirteenth Prince,

16:07.390 --> 16:08.240
you're…

16:08.720 --> 16:10.520
slaughtering innocent people!

16:15.200 --> 16:16.060
Your Highness!

16:17.360 --> 16:17.870
Your Highness!

16:17.870 --> 16:20.870
The Thirteenth Prince is the Son
of Heaven's Mandate.

16:32.630 --> 16:34.200
He may do as he pleases.

16:35.630 --> 16:37.400
Greetings to Princess Chun'er.

16:37.400 --> 16:38.730
So you're Zhao Chun'er.

16:39.000 --> 16:39.860
Your Highness,

16:40.270 --> 16:41.790
you should call me sister.

16:47.510 --> 16:48.480
Lift your head.

16:55.870 --> 16:56.720
This maid

16:56.960 --> 16:58.440
not only tore my clothes earlier,

16:58.440 --> 16:59.770
but also bumped into me.

17:00.030 --> 17:01.960
I was just about to settle
the score with her.

17:01.960 --> 17:04.369
It would be too merciful for
Your Highness to kill her.

17:04.369 --> 17:05.829
I want her to live in agony,

17:05.920 --> 17:07.119
unable to live or die.

17:08.109 --> 17:09.750
Your Highness, spare me!

17:09.880 --> 17:11.750
I've never met Your Highness before,

17:11.750 --> 17:12.480
how could I—

17:12.480 --> 17:13.270
Guards!

17:13.880 --> 17:15.540
Take her to the Zuixian Tower.

17:15.890 --> 17:18.200
Your Highness, have mercy!

17:19.400 --> 17:20.800
Spare me, Your Highness!

17:21.550 --> 17:23.680
Please, have mercy!

17:33.830 --> 17:35.550
Amusing. Most amusing.

17:41.790 --> 17:43.250
Your Highness is too kind,

17:43.440 --> 17:44.790
letting these servants

17:44.790 --> 17:46.550
rant and rave before you.

17:47.200 --> 17:48.160
Sister Chun,

17:54.510 --> 17:56.440
I've only heard others speak of you.

17:56.440 --> 17:58.570
I knew you were an interesting person,

17:59.590 --> 18:01.590
yet I never imagined you'd be so

18:02.400 --> 18:03.730
stunningly beautiful.

18:05.000 --> 18:07.260
I have something even more interesting.

18:09.030 --> 18:10.350
Would Your Highness care to

18:10.350 --> 18:11.880
come see it with me?

18:24.160 --> 18:25.510
It's just an ancestral shrine.

18:25.510 --> 18:27.310
What's so fascinating about it?

18:28.070 --> 18:29.800
Don't be hasty, Your Highness.

18:29.880 --> 18:30.610
Come with me.

18:34.210 --> 18:36.450
O Almighty Faceless God,

18:37.510 --> 18:39.790
hear the prayers of your believers.

18:39.790 --> 18:41.720
Reveal your true form to the world,

18:41.720 --> 18:43.310
guard the peace of all realms,

18:43.310 --> 18:45.030
and abide with me forever.

19:12.550 --> 19:13.410
On this statue…

19:14.350 --> 19:15.880
I see myself on this statue!

19:16.590 --> 19:18.000
I see my own face!

19:21.790 --> 19:23.960
Only those chosen by the Faceless God

19:23.960 --> 19:25.310
can see their own faces

19:25.310 --> 19:26.790
on this sacred statue.

19:28.240 --> 19:29.100
Your Highness,

19:29.960 --> 19:31.550
you are the Son of the Faceless God,

19:31.550 --> 19:33.610
the incarnation of the Faceless God.

19:34.480 --> 19:37.480
In the future, you shall not only be
King of Great Yong,

19:37.600 --> 19:39.550
but ruler of the entire world.

19:59.670 --> 20:00.510
General Qiu Lin!

20:00.510 --> 20:01.750
By the General's order!

20:01.750 --> 20:02.810
Step aside at once!

20:04.200 --> 20:05.070
By the King's order,

20:05.070 --> 20:07.070
General Qiu Lin is stationed
at the Northern Garrison.

20:07.070 --> 20:10.270
Without the King's decree,
he may not enter Ximengcheng.

20:28.550 --> 20:30.200
Without decrees from both the King
and General Meng En,

20:30.200 --> 20:31.660
no one is permitted entry.

20:36.960 --> 20:37.960
General Qiu Lin.

20:38.640 --> 20:39.720
Long time no see.

20:43.310 --> 20:44.310
General Meng,

20:45.640 --> 20:46.680
perfect timing.

20:46.830 --> 20:49.200
I left Ximengcheng less than a month ago.

20:49.640 --> 20:50.790
How is it that

20:51.030 --> 20:53.640
everything has changed so
drastically here?

20:53.790 --> 20:55.720
What do you mean, General Qiu Lin?

20:56.480 --> 20:57.680
I don't understand.

20:58.030 --> 20:59.510
Don't play dumb.

21:00.680 --> 21:02.400
You know full well the guards
of Ximengcheng

21:02.400 --> 21:03.960
once took orders from me.

21:04.350 --> 21:05.350
A month ago,

21:05.510 --> 21:08.200
I was ordered by the King
to garrison the north.

21:08.640 --> 21:10.030
Yet upon my return,

21:10.030 --> 21:12.680
I find Ximengcheng has fallen
into new hands.

21:14.110 --> 21:15.060
General Meng,

21:15.790 --> 21:17.070
tell me —

21:17.510 --> 21:20.590
who issued these ridiculous orders?

21:20.590 --> 21:22.510
Who freed my slaves?

21:22.510 --> 21:24.360
Who turned my own men

21:24.390 --> 21:25.980
into yours?

21:29.960 --> 21:31.760
All of this is by the King's will.

21:33.270 --> 21:35.130
I am only carrying out his orders.

21:36.200 --> 21:37.550
I intend to find out

21:38.270 --> 21:41.640
exactly what he's planning.

21:43.960 --> 21:45.890
General Qiu Lin, you know full well

21:46.030 --> 21:47.120
the consequences

21:47.480 --> 21:49.510
of trespassing in the inner palace

21:49.680 --> 21:51.280
without the King's command.

22:00.960 --> 22:02.020
I refuse to believe

22:02.350 --> 22:04.480
I will never be allowed to see the King.

22:20.310 --> 22:20.920
General,

22:22.270 --> 22:23.960
are we just going to leave like this?

22:23.960 --> 22:25.310
The more they block us,

22:25.510 --> 22:28.030
the more dirt they're hiding.

22:30.640 --> 22:31.770
Then what should we—

22:32.550 --> 22:33.400
In seven days,

22:33.400 --> 22:35.530
it will be Ximeng's Fire God Festival.

22:35.750 --> 22:37.750
King Ximeng will stand before his people

22:37.750 --> 22:39.010
to pray for blessings.

22:39.200 --> 22:40.880
They can hide for now,

22:41.350 --> 22:42.480
but on that day,

22:42.880 --> 22:44.640
no matter how great the secret,

22:45.030 --> 22:47.790
I will expose it to the light.

23:00.050 --> 23:02.360
[Seven Days Later, the Fire God
Sacrifice Ceremony]

23:02.590 --> 23:06.110
Today is Ximeng's Fire Worship Day.

23:06.750 --> 23:09.880
Our King Ximeng and
all people of Ximeng

23:10.030 --> 23:13.480
are blessed and protected
by the Red Fire God.

23:13.720 --> 23:18.720
Today we gather to thank
the gods for their gifts.

23:40.200 --> 23:43.160
The gods have accepted our offerings.

23:43.510 --> 23:47.070
Let King Ximeng pray for us.

24:16.680 --> 24:17.400
Traitors!

24:18.070 --> 24:20.030
How dare you impersonate King Ximeng!

24:20.030 --> 24:20.690
Seize them!

24:20.920 --> 24:22.440
Surround these men!

24:22.440 --> 24:23.550
Not one escapes!

24:28.720 --> 24:31.880
You think a mere mask lets you pretend
to be King Ximeng?

24:32.960 --> 24:34.420
Let's see what kind of fool

24:34.550 --> 24:36.400
you've put in his place.

24:42.670 --> 24:43.230
This…

24:46.380 --> 24:47.310
You tricked us!

25:06.940 --> 25:08.340
Zhuge Yue!

25:10.790 --> 25:12.350
Insolent Qiu Lin!

25:12.830 --> 25:14.240
How dare you rebel!

25:15.270 --> 25:17.000
I knew it was you.

25:17.880 --> 25:19.960
But you are only the King's shadow.

25:20.590 --> 25:21.880
The real King Ximeng

25:22.640 --> 25:24.440
died by your hands long ago, didn't he?

25:24.440 --> 25:25.070
Qiu Lin!

25:25.270 --> 25:26.960
How dare you question the King's identity!

25:26.960 --> 25:27.550
What?

25:27.680 --> 25:28.880
The King is dead?

25:28.880 --> 25:30.030
Slandering the King is a capital offense!

25:30.030 --> 25:30.960
Shut your mouth!

25:31.350 --> 25:33.150
Who do you think you are to speak?

25:33.590 --> 25:34.830
Foolish blind fool!

25:35.110 --> 25:36.350
Thirty years ago,

25:36.350 --> 25:38.440
I fought side by side with
King Ximeng right here,

25:38.440 --> 25:39.680
conquering this land.

25:39.680 --> 25:41.540
How could I not know his true face?

25:42.640 --> 25:43.590
Zhuge Yue,

25:44.000 --> 25:45.720
use your head.

25:47.060 --> 25:48.260
Can that face of yours

25:48.400 --> 25:50.590
possibly pass for a man past forty

25:50.590 --> 25:53.440
with a disfigured face?

25:56.090 --> 25:58.670
Ximengcheng has stood for
nearly twenty years.

25:58.670 --> 26:01.230
King Ximeng can't possibly be this young.

26:01.960 --> 26:03.200
But no one has ever seen

26:03.200 --> 26:04.590
what he really looks like.

26:04.590 --> 26:05.270
Maybe…

26:05.270 --> 26:07.310
he's different from ordinary people.

26:07.310 --> 26:09.030
They say King Ximeng
is horribly disfigured,

26:09.030 --> 26:10.070
which is why he wears a mask.

26:10.070 --> 26:11.200
But this face doesn't look

26:11.200 --> 26:12.590
frightening at all.

26:12.590 --> 26:13.980
I've seen this man before.

26:13.980 --> 26:15.240
He's really just a slave

26:15.240 --> 26:17.100
taken to be King Ximeng's double.

26:20.110 --> 26:20.880
Zhuge Yue,

26:22.680 --> 26:25.750
I knew you wouldn't admit it easily.

26:27.240 --> 26:29.790
So I've brought a friend for you.

26:31.350 --> 26:32.410
Bring him forward!

26:44.920 --> 26:45.790
Who is that?

26:46.510 --> 26:48.720
It's King of Lingyue!

26:49.030 --> 26:50.230
He's King of Lingyue!

26:50.510 --> 26:51.710
What's he doing here?

26:51.880 --> 26:52.680
That's right.

26:53.030 --> 26:54.750
This is King of Lingyue.

26:56.240 --> 26:58.300
When King Ximeng conquered this land,

26:58.300 --> 26:59.670
he took in his clan.

26:59.960 --> 27:03.490
He was fortunate enough to see
the King's face beneath the mask.

27:03.720 --> 27:06.680
Today we shall have him identify

27:07.310 --> 27:10.200
who this man truly is.

27:13.640 --> 27:15.100
You've heard everything.

27:15.640 --> 27:16.230
Speak.

27:18.350 --> 27:21.960
Is this King Ximeng you knew?

27:35.270 --> 27:37.440
Speak truthfully,

27:38.950 --> 27:41.220
and these delicious buns are all yours.

27:41.820 --> 27:44.070
Tell me — who is this man?

27:44.160 --> 27:45.270
Do you recognize him?

27:45.270 --> 27:47.030
Is he King Ximeng you knew?

27:47.640 --> 27:48.510
Speak! Speak!

27:51.920 --> 27:52.550
Speak!

27:53.460 --> 27:54.550
He is not King Ximeng.

27:54.550 --> 27:55.680
Louder!

27:55.680 --> 27:57.110
He is not King Ximeng!

28:00.150 --> 28:00.910
Zhuge Yue.

28:00.930 --> 28:02.000
You heard him.

28:03.000 --> 28:05.110
Now everyone who has seen
His Majesty's true face

28:05.110 --> 28:06.920
has denied your identity.

28:07.550 --> 28:09.000
What else can you argue?

28:35.370 --> 28:38.090
Do you still remember who you are?

29:10.920 --> 29:11.560
Li.

29:12.960 --> 29:13.790
I'm sorry.

29:15.590 --> 29:16.960
Can you forgive me?

29:17.570 --> 29:19.330
At the highest point of Mount Wumu,

29:19.330 --> 29:22.170
we were to meet at sunrise.
But I came too late.

29:22.880 --> 29:24.110
Li, I'm sorry.

29:25.110 --> 29:26.900
At the highest point of Mount Wumu,

29:26.900 --> 29:29.430
we were to meet at sunrise.
But I came too late.

29:30.030 --> 29:31.310
Please forgive me.

29:32.400 --> 29:33.720
King of Lingyue has long lost his sanity.

29:33.720 --> 29:34.960
Li, I'm sorry.

29:35.960 --> 29:37.030
I came too late.

29:37.440 --> 29:38.370
How can his words

29:38.880 --> 29:39.790
be trusted?

29:39.970 --> 29:41.010
I came too late.

29:41.990 --> 29:43.270
Li, I'm sorry.

29:43.300 --> 29:44.070
Qiu Lin.

29:44.920 --> 29:46.510
Using the words of a madman

29:46.920 --> 29:48.320
to overturn King Ximeng,

29:48.400 --> 29:50.060
what are you really plotting?

29:50.680 --> 29:52.310
Useless lunatic!

30:11.630 --> 30:13.630
I have fought in wars for many years.

30:14.920 --> 30:16.680
I have brought unnecessary tragedies

30:16.680 --> 30:18.240
to many tribes.

30:20.110 --> 30:20.750
But now,

30:21.830 --> 30:23.510
Ximeng has reformed.

30:24.180 --> 30:26.690
From now on, not only the Lingyue Clan,

30:27.200 --> 30:29.110
but all other tribes
may keep their own customs

30:29.110 --> 30:31.110
and govern their own strongholds.

30:33.440 --> 30:34.030
Except

30:35.070 --> 30:37.000
that slavery is no longer allowed,

30:38.440 --> 30:40.200
everything else remains the same.

30:40.200 --> 30:41.790
Annual tribute will be cut in half.

30:41.790 --> 30:42.750
Cut in half?

30:42.750 --> 30:43.590
Is it true?

30:43.750 --> 30:44.480
No idea.

30:45.110 --> 30:45.720
It is true?

30:51.670 --> 30:53.930
I just came from General Qiu Lin's estate

30:54.350 --> 30:56.010
and found something strange.

30:56.960 --> 30:59.760
The abolition of slavery
in Ximeng is known to all.

30:59.830 --> 31:02.490
How is it that you
know nothing of this, General,

31:02.550 --> 31:04.510
and yet keep hundreds of slaves

31:04.720 --> 31:06.310
on your own estate?

31:06.880 --> 31:10.190
General, are you openly defying
the new policies of Ximeng,

31:10.190 --> 31:11.990
or do you have some other motive?

31:12.160 --> 31:13.160
New policies?

31:14.110 --> 31:16.160
When even King Ximeng is a fake,

31:16.480 --> 31:18.590
what kind of darn new policy is there?

31:18.590 --> 31:21.110
Are you questioning
whether King Ximeng is real,

31:21.110 --> 31:23.370
or are you unwilling to abolish slavery,

31:23.400 --> 31:26.350
resenting that King Ximeng
has harmed your interests,

31:26.350 --> 31:29.750
and using this as an excuse
to commit regicide and rebellion?

31:29.880 --> 31:31.510
That's bullshit!

31:34.020 --> 31:34.590
Let's go.

31:38.880 --> 31:40.200
Long live the King!

31:40.400 --> 31:44.240
May all tribes of Ximeng
unite as one and prosper for generations!

31:44.510 --> 31:46.350
Long live the King!

31:47.790 --> 31:49.350
Ximeng has reformed.

31:50.240 --> 31:50.900
From now on,

31:51.960 --> 31:54.090
there is no need to kneel in obeisance.

32:04.640 --> 32:06.200
Long live the King!

32:06.440 --> 32:10.920
May all tribes of Ximeng unite
as one and prosper for generations!

32:11.000 --> 32:14.410
United as one, prospering for generations!

32:17.620 --> 32:19.950
[Six years ago]

32:50.070 --> 32:51.400
Run!

33:01.520 --> 33:02.510
I learned this game

33:02.510 --> 33:04.920
from a foreign merchant
newly arrived from the Western Regions.

33:04.920 --> 33:07.160
The wolves in our hunting grounds
have been starved for 3 days,

33:07.160 --> 33:08.360
their eyes already red with hunger.

33:08.360 --> 33:09.840
We can shoot these beasts,

33:10.270 --> 33:12.400
or we can shoot other people's slaves.

33:12.570 --> 33:14.090
So, is it interesting?

33:47.360 --> 33:48.160
Zhuge Huai.

33:48.680 --> 33:50.440
Isn't this game a bit too cruel?

33:50.670 --> 33:52.510
They are just a few young slave girls.

33:52.510 --> 33:54.240
If Your Highness can't bear it,

33:54.240 --> 33:56.070
I will personally visit another day

33:56.070 --> 33:57.400
and send you a new batch.

33:57.590 --> 33:59.920
Our Zhuge family has plenty.

34:06.310 --> 34:07.000
Run!

34:16.730 --> 34:17.409
Run!

34:21.969 --> 34:22.739
Zhuge Huai!

34:22.800 --> 34:24.130
Have you lost your mind?

34:25.090 --> 34:25.920
Run!

34:46.000 --> 34:47.060
Heir Apparent Yan,

34:47.480 --> 34:48.590
what do you mean by this?

34:48.590 --> 34:50.130
Since this is an archery contest,

34:50.130 --> 34:53.340
killing and saving
with arrows are the same.

35:09.450 --> 35:10.780
Bite her! Bite her!

35:45.960 --> 35:46.960
Heir Apparent Yan.

35:46.960 --> 35:49.030
Are you deliberately making
things difficult for me?

35:49.030 --> 35:50.690
We each rely on our own skills.

35:50.730 --> 35:54.190
Young Master Huai, why lose
your temper out of embarrassment?

36:05.510 --> 36:06.070
Run!

36:07.230 --> 36:07.840
Great!

36:09.070 --> 36:09.730
Be careful!

36:20.230 --> 36:21.030
Zhuge Yue.

36:21.920 --> 36:24.250
Now this warm sunlight of equality for all

36:24.390 --> 36:27.650
has finally melted the frozen ground
once bound in chains.

36:33.230 --> 36:34.190
These medicines

36:34.510 --> 36:36.170
were all prepared by Xiao Ran.

36:36.190 --> 36:37.920
Make sure he takes them on time.

36:38.030 --> 36:39.710
Only then can
the Blood on Snow poison in his body

36:39.710 --> 36:41.040
be completely cleared.

36:43.110 --> 36:43.960
I entrust

36:45.150 --> 36:46.750
King of Lingyue to your care.

36:53.000 --> 36:53.550
Let's go.

36:54.030 --> 36:55.090
I'm not going back.

36:55.360 --> 36:56.490
I'm going to find Li.

36:58.320 --> 36:59.250
King of Lingyue.

36:59.360 --> 36:59.800
Here.

37:01.150 --> 37:01.960
Li is

37:02.480 --> 37:03.920
waiting for you at Mount Wumu.

37:03.920 --> 37:05.400
She has been waiting
for you for a long time.

37:05.400 --> 37:06.800
If you don't go back soon,

37:06.960 --> 37:08.190
she will be angry.

37:09.190 --> 37:10.050
I'm going back.

37:10.680 --> 37:12.540
Li is waiting for me at Mount Wumu.

37:12.920 --> 37:14.320
I'm going back to find Li.

37:14.640 --> 37:15.920
I'm going back to find Li.

37:15.920 --> 37:17.320
I'm going back to find Li.

37:19.230 --> 37:20.630
I'm going back to find Li!

37:21.030 --> 37:21.560
Let's go.

37:21.710 --> 37:23.110
I'm going back to find Li!

37:24.760 --> 37:25.670
I'm going back.

37:26.510 --> 37:27.920
I'm going back to find Li!

37:30.220 --> 37:30.800
Shiyi and I

37:30.800 --> 37:33.860
will escort them
to the mountain pass ahead and return.

37:47.440 --> 37:49.170
Why do you think King of Lingyue

37:49.510 --> 37:51.440
gave me the green-eyed bird?

37:53.550 --> 37:55.400
The Queen of Lingyue once told me

37:55.880 --> 37:58.070
that in their language,
the green-eyed bird

37:58.070 --> 37:59.280
means trust.

37:59.920 --> 38:01.880
The gemstone used for its eyes

38:02.320 --> 38:04.320
is a rare stone
of the Lingyue Clan.

38:05.320 --> 38:07.120
It can test a lover's sincerity.

38:08.320 --> 38:10.050
Each person in a couple has one.

38:10.320 --> 38:12.320
It's because if either of them lies,

38:13.110 --> 38:15.480
the stone will glow.

38:16.880 --> 38:18.210
If you don't believe it,

38:19.590 --> 38:20.760
we can test it.

38:26.000 --> 38:27.660
Let me ask you a few questions.

38:27.880 --> 38:29.740
You must answer them truthfully.

38:30.280 --> 38:30.810
Alright.

38:34.320 --> 38:35.110
Zhuge Yue.

38:36.710 --> 38:37.630
Up to now,

38:38.550 --> 38:40.210
how many women have you liked?

38:44.150 --> 38:44.800
Three.

38:46.280 --> 38:47.280
Three?

38:50.510 --> 38:51.150
The first

38:51.510 --> 38:53.590
was a maidservant
from Qingshan Manor of Great Yong,

38:53.590 --> 38:54.400
named Xing.

38:57.480 --> 38:58.190
The second?

38:58.590 --> 38:59.280
The second

39:00.590 --> 39:02.840
was the leader
of the Xiuli Army in Great Yan,

39:02.840 --> 39:03.960
named Chu Qiao.

39:06.230 --> 39:07.360
And the last one?

39:08.360 --> 39:09.480
The last one

39:10.440 --> 39:12.440
is now my Queen Ximeng.

39:19.000 --> 39:20.260
Now it's my turn to ask.

39:21.400 --> 39:21.920
Xing.

39:23.150 --> 39:25.680
Up to now, how many
men have you liked in total?

39:25.840 --> 39:26.440
Three.

39:28.920 --> 39:30.450
The first was free and wild,

39:30.800 --> 39:32.130
bold and unrestrained.

39:32.240 --> 39:33.770
He was an eagle of the skies.

39:37.190 --> 39:37.840
Yan Xun.

39:39.230 --> 39:40.090
And the second?

39:40.550 --> 39:41.320
The second

39:42.110 --> 39:44.590
was charming and carefree, full of spirit.

39:46.510 --> 39:47.230
Sadly,

39:48.400 --> 39:49.630
he died young.

39:50.000 --> 39:51.280
You liked Li Ce too?

39:54.840 --> 39:55.840
I was lying to you.

39:56.880 --> 39:58.740
I didn't like the first two at all.

39:59.590 --> 40:00.920
I only like the last one.

40:02.800 --> 40:04.150
He is

40:05.190 --> 40:06.920
a block of ice,

40:07.480 --> 40:10.210
cold and aloof,
utterly clueless about romance.

40:11.550 --> 40:13.480
Who's this
cold and clueless block of ice

40:13.480 --> 40:16.800
you are talking about?

40:18.710 --> 40:20.150
He's right

40:20.880 --> 40:22.320
in front of me.

40:23.630 --> 40:26.230
He's also a strikingly handsome man,

40:27.150 --> 40:28.960
graceful and refined,

40:30.880 --> 40:32.210
yet still a block of ice.

40:35.840 --> 40:37.320
Why are you so petty?

40:37.580 --> 40:38.190
I learned it from you,

40:38.190 --> 40:40.000
you clueless block of ice.

41:12.260 --> 41:15.690
[Yunlai Inn]

41:28.670 --> 41:29.530
General Cheng.

41:33.280 --> 41:34.190
Your Highness.

41:47.030 --> 41:49.090
This was picked up from Tubu that day.

41:49.190 --> 41:50.990
I forgot to return it at the time.

41:51.000 --> 41:54.000
Today I came especially
to return it to Your Highness.

42:00.030 --> 42:01.070
You mended this?

42:08.280 --> 42:09.080
In the future,

42:11.150 --> 42:13.350
please be more careful, Your Highness.

42:13.710 --> 42:15.440
If there is nothing important,

42:17.070 --> 42:18.880
it would be best not to leave the palace.

42:18.880 --> 42:21.280
If anything were
to happen to Your Highness,

42:21.280 --> 42:23.280
it would also be
His Majesty's loss.

42:23.480 --> 42:24.340
That would mean

42:25.190 --> 42:26.710
it is our responsibility as well.

42:26.710 --> 42:28.240
You called me out specially

42:28.990 --> 42:30.440
just to say this?

42:36.630 --> 42:37.190
Yes.

42:43.550 --> 42:45.950
I understand what you mean, General Cheng.

42:58.590 --> 43:00.320
The jade pendant has been broken.

43:00.320 --> 43:01.380
Just throw it away.

43:14.550 --> 43:15.410
Your Highness.

43:15.590 --> 43:17.320
Why did you come out so quickly?

43:17.320 --> 43:20.780
You left behind the cloak
you meant to return to General Cheng.

43:48.190 --> 43:50.800
I heard Ximeng has
discovered a black gold mine.

43:50.800 --> 43:52.510
Can you really give up everything

43:52.510 --> 43:54.440
and run away with that slave girl?

43:54.440 --> 43:56.150
Then shouldn't the wound
from Qingshan Manor

43:56.150 --> 43:57.630
heal as well?

43:57.880 --> 43:58.590
Jing Xiaoliu.

43:58.590 --> 43:59.650
Why can't you do it?

44:00.840 --> 44:02.500
Why must you push me like this?

44:02.630 --> 44:03.760
Please forget me.

44:04.320 --> 44:05.530
Just pretend that I really

44:05.530 --> 44:06.800
died in the frozen lake.
